OL,3,CPost Office top team had 'bunker
OL,4,Cmentality' to questions about Horizon
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FA lawyer has said there was a "bunker
OL,8,Fmentality" among staff in relation to
OL,9,Fthe media's coverage of the Horizon IT
OL,10,Fsystem and subpostmaster's distrust of
OL,11,Fit.
OL,13,FRodric Williams, who joined the
OL,14,Forganisation as a litigation lawyer in
OL,15,F2012, was asked at the on Thursday
OL,16,Fabout an email sent to the Post Office
OL,17,Fby journalist Nick Wallis in 2014.
