OL,3,CPost Office top team had 'bunker
OL,4,Cmentality' to questions about Horizon
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FIn the email, Mr Wallis asked when was
OL,8,Fthe last time the Post Office did any
OL,9,Fresearch into how satisfied
OL,10,Fsubpostmasters were with the Horizon
OL,11,Fsystem.
OL,13,FIn a response to colleagues about Mr
OL,14,FWallis's email, Mr Williams said: "We
OL,15,Fdon't need to do research on Horizon `
OL,16,Fit's the system we provide to our
OL,17,Fagents and require them to use. If
OL,18,Fagents don't like it, they can choose
OL,19,Fnot to provide services for us.
OL,26,@vD@cOU
