OL,3,CPost Office top team had 'bunker
OL,4,Cmentality' to questions about Horizon
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,F"The vast majority of our agents and
OL,8,Fother users work with it just fine,
OL,9,Fand we're not required to bespoke our
OL,10,Fpoint of sale accounting system to the
OL,11,Fwhims of each individual agent."
OL,13,FMr Williams was asked if it was his
OL,14,Fview at the time that "subpostmasters
OL,15,Fcould either use Horizon or leave," to
OL,16,Fwhich he replied "yes."
OL,18,FHe was asked if he meant "like it or
OL,19,Flump it".
