OL,3,CPost Office top team had 'bunker
OL,4,Cmentality' to questions about Horizon
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,F"Not necessarily," he said, "it is the
OL,8,Fsystem that is used across many
OL,9,Fthousands of branches, and I think
OL,10,Ftens of thousands of terminals. That
OL,11,Fis the system the Post Office
OL,12,Fprovided."
OL,14,FHowever, he said he did not believe
OL,15,Fthere was an "obligation" on the Post
OL,16,FOffice to do market research on
OL,17,FHorizon's users.
