OL,3,CPost Office top team had 'bunker
OL,4,Cmentality' to questions about Horizon
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FHe told the inquiry there was a
OL,8,F"bunker mentality" among the
OL,9,Forganisation's staff in relation to
OL,10,Fthe media's treatment of Horizon.
OL,12,F"I don't know if I can speak for
OL,13,Fsenior management but I do think
OL,14,Fcertainly where I was sitting it did
OL,15,Ffeel a bit bunker mentality, yes," he
OL,16,Ftold the inquiry.
OL,18,FHe was asked if he was in the bunker.
OL,19,F"I probably was, yes," he said.
