OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FMr Williams was also asked about his
OL,8,Fattitude towards Tim McCormack, a
OL,9,Fformer subpostmaster who tried to warn
OL,10,Fthe organisation about the Horizon
OL,11,Fsystem.
OL,13,FIn 2015, Mr McCormack wrote to Post
OL,14,FOffice CEO Paula Vennells warning her
OL,15,Fthat he had "clear and unquestionable
OL,16,Fevidence of an intermittent bug in
OL,17,FHorizon that can and does cause
OL,18,Fthousands of pounds in losses to
OL,19,Fsubpostmasters".
