OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FHe said it was her "last chance" to
OL,8,Faccept that "what I have been telling
OL,9,Fyou these last few years is true".
OL,11,FHe invited Ms Vennells to visit a
OL,12,Fbranch with him, so he could show her
OL,13,Fthe evidence.
OL,15,FThe email was forwarded to Mr
OL,16,FWilliams, who told colleagues that
OL,17,Fthey should ask Mr McCormack to send
OL,18,Fthem the information.
