OL,7,F"Generally, my view is that this guy
OL,8,Fis a bluffer, who keeps expecting us
OL,9,Fto march to his tune," he wrote in
OL,10,Femail to colleagues.
OL,12,F"I don't think we should do that, but
OL,13,Finstead respond with a straight bat."
